00:10:04.390 --> 00:10:07.840
Campaign in AdWords enabled
already, then you don't need

00:10:07.840 --> 00:10:08.320
to do this.

00:10:08.320 --> 00:10:10.290
It's automatic.

00:10:10.290 --> 00:10:12.640
Pretty cool.

00:10:12.640 --> 00:10:14.620
And it's not just about getting
your content into

00:10:14.620 --> 00:10:15.390
Google Search.

00:10:15.390 --> 00:10:19.310
It's about getting your content
across all of Google.

