more followers you have, the

00:12:17.590 --> 00:12:20.930
bigger opportunity for people
to discover your brand.

00:12:20.930 --> 00:12:25.450
And of course, in order to get
that great effect and to

00:12:25.450 --> 00:12:28.580
increase your imprint in Google
Search, you want to

00:12:28.580 --> 00:12:31.455
send app activities via
Google+ Sign In

00:12:31.455 --> 00:12:33.095
to Google as well.

