learned from them.

00:13:45.230 --> 00:13:46.900
And just copy this.

00:13:46.900 --> 00:13:49.780
It's a playbook for
a successful page.

00:13:49.780 --> 00:13:52.420
So starting out, one of the
things that we've noticed

00:13:52.420 --> 00:13:56.710
they've done is they have an
animated GIF as their cover

00:13:56.710 --> 00:13:59.810
photo, which really
makes that pop.

00:13:59.810 --> 00:14:04.190
And their magic formula
is simple.

00:14:04.190 --> 00:14:07.390
They have one attractive and
simple photo per post.

00:14:07.390 --> 00:14:11.160
Sometimes it's a video, but
mostly it's a photo.

00:14:11.160 --> 00:14:14.250
They have, like, one line
of text and maybe

00:14:14.250 --> 00:14:17.030
a hashtag or two.

00:14:17.030 --> 00:14:22.360
And the hashtags now appear at
the top of your post you

00:14:22.360 --> 00:14:24.620
create, as well as
related hashtags.

00:14:24.620 --> 00:14:27.570
So they can be an important
way for your content to be

00:14:27.570 --> 00:14:29.390
discovered as well.

00:14:29.390 --> 00:14:31.130
And they include offers
in their posts.

00:14:31.130 --> 00:14:35.030
It's kind of hard to tell from
this, but this is an offer.

00:14:35.030 --> 00:14:37.940
And you feel good about gifting
it to your loved ones

00:14:37.940 --> 00:14:39.030
by resharing it.

00:14:39.030 --> 00:14:43.860
And you get material value
from the post as well.

00:14:43.860 --> 00:14:48.270
And they have authentic photos,
not stock photos.

00:14:48.270 --> 00:14:52.090
So it looks like they put more
thought into it rather than

00:14:52.090 --> 00:14:53.870
just posting without thinking.

00:14:53.870 --> 00:14:56.920
And they're asking the
community questions.

00:14:56.920 --> 00:15:00.350
So it really creates
that interaction.

00:15:00.350 --> 00:15:05.480
And they're also posting
infographics, which can also

00:15:05.480 --> 00:15:07.730
be superviral.

00:15:07.730 --> 00:15:09.970
And they have occasion
driven posts.

00:15:09.970 --> 00:15:13.310
So this is a post from the
Kentucky Derby that they did.

00:15:13.310 --> 00:15:14.830
They've also done some
for Mother's

00:15:14.830 --> 00:15:16.670
Day and other occasions.

00:15:16.670 --> 00:15:21.990
But it really captures that
top of mind, feel good

00:15:21.990 --> 00:15:24.490
sentiment the audience has.

00:15:24.490 --> 00:15:27.280
So you guys, one recommendation
is to have a

00:15:27.280 --> 00:15:31.570
posting calendar that mirrors
special occasions or topical

00:15:31.570 --> 00:15:35.890
news events related to your
brand and business.

00:15:35.890 --> 00:15:40.520
So cute and resharable posts
create virality.

00:15:40.520 --> 00:15:42.670
It's very clever thinking.

00:15:42.670 --> 00:15:45.340
Your first emotional response
is to want to share it.

00:15:48.820 --> 00:15:52.790
And one of the most effective
ways to grow your followers is

00:15:52.790 --> 00:15:56.100
by adding the Google+
badge to your site.

00:15:56.100 --> 00:15:57.430
Hopefully we've all now learned

00:15:57.430 --> 00:15:58.980
the value of a follower.

00:15:58.980 --> 00:16:04.160
And it comes in a variety of
shapes and sizes, but at its

00:16:04.160 --> 00:16:08.390
core, it lets people know that
you're on Google+ and add you

00:16:08.390 --> 00:16:09.670
to their Circles directly.

00:16:12.180 --> 00:16:15.390
And you should add the badge,
not just to your website, but

00:16:15.390 --> 00:16:22.420
to your emails, your blog, any
offline campaigns that you're

00:16:22.420 --> 00:16:27.250
doing, or anything that you
have, in-store signage.

00:16:27.250 --> 00:16:29.790
In this example, Britney Spears
plastered it on her

00:16:29.790 --> 00:16:33.000
homepage of her website.

00:16:33.000 --> 00:16:37.200
Your page should be part of
your business strategy.

00:16:37.200 --> 00:16:40.710
And you can also advertise, if
you'd like to also help gain

00:16:40.710 --> 00:16:46.140
more followers, on our GDN or
in Google Search as well.

00:16:46.140 --> 00:16:49.710
And what we found is that top
publishers who installed the

00:16:49.710 --> 00:16:53.570
badge grew their audience
by 38% on average.

00:16:53.570 --> 00:16:55.670
That's pretty amazing for
such minimal work.

00:16:55.670 --> 00:16:57.360
The badge is so easy to add.

00:16:57.360 --> 00:17:00.600
You should do it today.

00:17:00.600 --> 00:17:02.640
And you really want to give
people a reason to

00:17:02.640 --> 00:17:05.380
come to your page.

00:17:05.380 --> 00:17:09.000
It's just a more natural way to
get more followers, is to

00:17:09.000 --> 00:17:13.430
just drive them to some sort of
content or programming that

00:17:13.430 --> 00:17:15.569
you're doing, like
with a Hangout.

00:17:15.569 --> 00:17:18.119
So it feels more natural to
tell them to come and join

00:17:18.119 --> 00:17:20.060
your page if you have something
going on there.

00:17:23.520 --> 00:17:26.400
Which brings us to
our next point of

00:17:26.400 --> 00:17:27.740
engagement and Hangouts.

