So now that we've learned what
you should be doing on Google+

00:17:30.790 --> 00:17:33.790
to help get discovered, let's
shift to talk about how

00:17:33.790 --> 00:17:37.440
Google+ is also enabling you
to create deeper and more

00:17:37.440 --> 00:17:41.130
personal relationships
with your users.

