00:21:02.820 --> 00:21:08.320
So this February, Topshop
reinvented its fashion show

00:21:08.320 --> 00:21:11.460
and simultaneously democratized
the thrill of

00:21:11.460 --> 00:21:15.720
London Fashion Week, something
